OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening and night with outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain, this most persistent and
OL,8,Fheaviest across the Southern Uplands.
OL,9,FDrier along the east coast. Fresh
OL,10,Fsoutherly winds, strong along the
OL,11,FSolway coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FCloudy in the morning with
OL,14,Frain gradually dying out. The
OL,15,Fafternoon will be dry with some bright
OL,16,For sunny spells, perhaps a little rain
OL,17,Fat first across the Borders.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
